  <rte>
    <name>Grisedale Pike and Crag Hill from Braithwaite</name>
    <desc>This lake District walk is a circuit of Coledale starting with an ascent of Grisedale Pike and followed by a superb section of high level walking before reaching Crag Hill.</desc>
